title: Episode 265: Unblock Me Please (Feat. City Girls)
itunes:title: Episode 265: Unblock Me Please (Feat. City Girls)
description:
The City Girls are here this week to promote their latest album “City On Lock." The ladies cover a range of topics including how they each argue with their men, how to properly ask for something you want, blocking your friends on social media, and much more. JT even opens up about the time the tricked a guy for a new car! Enjoy!
